trong>Principal Front-End Engineer</strong> at <strong>Porto Tech Center - Jumia</strong>, focused on building scalable, high-performance web applications.<br><br>I lead front-end architecture, define technical direction, and promote best practices while leveraging modern frameworks and tooling.<br><br>Driven by performance and user experience, I collaborate across teams to deliver robust, user-centric solutions and tackle complex engineering challenges.</p></div></div></section><section class="-mx-6 flex flex-col items-center border-t border-white/80 bg-white/5 px-6 py-16 text-center dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-zinc-900/15"><div class="w-full max-w-sm text-left sm:max-w-xl @2xl:max-w-xl"><div class="mb-12 sm:flex sm:items-center sm:justify-between"><h2 style="--delay:200ms;" class="animate-base op-low animate-fade-in-down">Professional Experience</h2><span style="--delay:250ms;" class="animate-base op-low animate-fade-in-down mt-2 flex items-center gap-2 sm:mt-0"><span class="hidden sm:inline-block"><div class="relative inline-block text-[0px]"><label aria-label="Compact timeline" class="inline-flex cursor-pointer items-center text-[0px] "><input type="checkbox" aria-label="Compact timeline" class="peer sr-only"><span class="relative flex h-5 w-9 shrink-0 items-center rounded-full bg-zinc-300 p-0.5 shadow-sm transition-colors peer-checked:justify-end peer-checked:bg-zinc-900 peer-hover:bg-zinc-400 peer-checked:peer-hover:bg-zinc-800 peer-focus-visible:outline-2 peer-focus-visible:outline-offset-1 peer-focus-visible:outline-zinc-400 dark:bg-zinc-600 dark:peer-checked:bg-white dark:peer-hover:bg-zinc-500 dark:peer-checked:peer-hover:bg-zinc-200 dark:peer-focus-visible:outline-zinc-500"><span class="h-4 w-4 rounded-full bg-white shadow-sm transition-all dark:bg-zinc-900"></span></span></label></div></span><span class="inline sm:hidden"><label aria-label="Compact timeline" class="inline-flex cursor-pointer items-center text-[0px] "><input type="checkbox" aria-label="C